{
  "stem": "26142.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, we are coming back to before Yom Kippur of 1941, '42. '41-- I'm talking about the Yiddish calendar, the Hebrew calendar, which is [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, they are two-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A day before Yom Kippur-- and-- and here in my-- in my memoirs, I have the-- the equivalent day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It-- you know, it's usually either-- either at the end of September, or it could be I don't-- I have the exact date.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got a-- a driver in there, because this was a long-- a long-- a longer trip to-- to-- and we were talking that we will go back to the city of Stanislau.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this driver was to take us where we got on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was taking us not directly with the main highways.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was taking us with-- with side roads.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he brought us close to the city of-- in a-- in a village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't remember the name of the village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He-- he said, this is as far as I'm going to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We paid him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we started walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this is a day before Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] No.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right-- a day before Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we came to this little village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, how did we-- we walked in a line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was my brother Tsvi and I walked-- single lines in-- in a-- in motion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The children will walk behind us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and we had made up some signs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we were apart about 100 meters or so that we can see each other in case we see military trucks or gendarmes, to get off the highway-- to-- to-- to-- to get off.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we-- we came to this little village.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
